quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  6,74,"Jaŋto] tuma nde Ibraa hiima maakannoo ben makko Aazara: "Ea jogitoto sanamuuji deweteeɗi?" Pellet, min miɗo yi'e an e yimɓe maa ɓen,e ndeer majjere ɓanngunde!".(feeñnd)"
  6,75,"Ko wano noon Min kolliri Ibraahiima laamuuji kammuuli ɗiin e leydi ndi, e fii yo o jeye e yananaaɓe ɓeen."
  6,76,"Nde jemma on niɓɓitunoo e makko, o tini hoodere, o maaki : "Ndee ɗoo ko joomi am!"ɓaawo nde mutii, o maaki : "Mi yiɗaa mutooɓe ɓeen"."
  6,77,"Nde o yii lewru ndu no jalbi, o maaki : "Nduu ɗoo ko joomi am!" ɓaawo ndu mutii, o maaki : "Si Joom am fewnaani kam, ma mi jeye e yimɓe majjuɓe ɓeen"."
  6,78,"Nde o yinoo naange ngen no jalbi, o maaki : "Ngee ɗoo ko joomi am! Ko ngee ɗoo ɓuri mawnude" ɓaawo nge mutii, o maaki : "Ko onon yo yimɓe am, min ko mi kisɗo e kon ko cikoton"."
  6,79,"Min dey mi fewtinirii yeeso am ngo e on Takɗo kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin ; ooñiiɗo=haniifiyanke, min mi jeyaaka e sirkooɓe ɓen.(renndinooɓe Alla e goɗɗum)."
  6,80,"Yimɓe makko ɓen mbennji mo ; o maaki : "E on mbennjay kam fii Alla, gooŋɗii le o fewnii kam? Mi hulataa kon ko kafidoton e Makko, si wanaa nde Joomi am muuyi huunde. Joomi am yaajanii kala huunde ganndal. E on mbaactotaako?"
  6,81,"Ko holno mi kulirta kon ko kafiduɗon on kulaali onon le on kafidii Alla e huunde nde O Jippinanaali on hujja? Ko honnde e peɗle ɗiɗi ɓuri haan dude e(hoolaare) deeƴere? Si on laatike annduɓe."